# Kubernetes Upgrade Readiness Assessor

A CLI tool that combines **deterministic kubectl analysis** and **LLM-powered reasoning** to assess whether a Kubernetes cluster is ready for a version upgrade.

## Demo

```
python kube_assessor.py -s 1.34 -t 1.35 -o report.md
```

```
============================================================
  Kubernetes Upgrade Readiness Assessor
  1.34 → 1.35
============================================================

Collecting cluster state...
  [1/10] kubectl version
  [2/10] kubectl cluster-info
  ...
Running static analysis...
  Removed APIs    : 0
  Deprecated APIs : 0
  CRDs            : 6
  Webhooks        : 2
  Readiness Score : 60/100
  Confidence      : 95%

Calling LLM (OpenRouter)...
Generating report...

✅ Report written to: report.md
```

