Generated : 2026-07-03T11:53:17Z
Source    : v1.34
Target    : v1.35

## Executive Summary

**UPGRADE DECISION : NOT RECOMMENDED**

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Readiness Score | 60/100 |
| Confidence      | 95%   |

### Admission Webhooks

> ⚠️ 2 webhook(s) with FailurePolicy=Fail — these can block all
> deployments if they become unavailable during upgrade.

## LLM Expert Analysis

### Required Actions Before Upgrade
1. Verify exact cert-manager version and confirm 1.35 compatibility
2. Prepare rollback procedure including cert-manager downgrade path
3. Backup all CRDs and cluster state
...
```

